  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK270">
<l>ilarpala rākiya kāraṇa nōṟpār</l>
<l>cilarpalar nōlā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Because there are few who practise austerity and many who do not, there are many destitute and few rich in this world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
